content:
{
  "sentences": [
    {
      "text": "我還會不太會說中文，但是我在慢慢學。",
      "pinyin": "Wǒ hái bù tài huì shuō Zhōngwén, dànshì wǒ zài mànmàn xué.",
      "pinyin_numeric": "wo3 hai2 bu4 tai4 hui4 shuo1 Zhong1wen2, dan4shi4 wo3 zai4 man4man4 xue2.",
      "translation_en": "I still can't speak Chinese very well, but I'm learning slowly.",
      "translation_ko": "저는 아직 중국어를 잘 못하지만, 천천히 배우고 있어요."
    },
    {
      "text": "他還會不太會寫字，可是已經進步很多了。",
      "pinyin": "Tā hái bù tài huì xiě zì, kěshì yǐjīng jìnbù hěn duō le.",
      "pinyin_numeric": "ta1 hai2 bu4 tai4 hui4 xie3 zi4, ke3shi4 yi3jing1 jin4bu4 hen3 duo1 le0.",
      "translation_en": "He still can't write characters very well, but he has already improved a lot.",
      "translation_ko": "그는 아직 글자를 잘 쓰지 못하지만, 이미 많이 발전했어요."
    },
    {
      "text": "我妹妹還不太會騎腳踏車，所以她每天練習。",
      "pinyin": "Wǒ mèimei hái bù tài huì qí jiǎotàchē, suǒyǐ tā měitiān liànxí.",
      "pinyin_numeric": "wo3 mei4mei hai2 bu4 tai4 hui4 qi2 jiao3ta4che1, suo3yi3 ta1 mei3tian1 lian4xi2.",
      "translation_en": "My younger sister still can't ride a bike very well, so she practices every day.",
      "translation_ko": "제 여동생은 아직 자전거를 잘 타지 못해서 매일 연습해요."
    },
    {
      "text": "你還會不太會煮菜嗎？要不要我教你？",
      "pinyin": "Nǐ hái bù tài huì zhǔ cài ma? Yào bù yào wǒ jiāo nǐ?",
      "pinyin_numeric": "ni3 hai2 bu4 tai4 hui4 zhu3 cai4 ma0? yao4 bu4 yao4 wo3 jiao1 ni3?",
      "translation_en": "Do you still not know how to cook very well? Do you want me to teach you?",
      "translation_ko": "아직 요리를 잘 못하세요? 제가 가르쳐 드릴까요?"
    },
    {
      "text": "我朋友還不太會開車，所以他都搭捷運上班。",
      "pinyin": "Wǒ péngyou hái bù tài huì kāi chē, suǒyǐ tā dōu dā jiéyùn shàngbān.",
      "pinyin_numeric": "wo3 peng2you hai2 bu4 tai4 hui4 kai1 che1, suo3yi3 ta1 dou1 da1 jie2yun4 shang4ban1.",
      "translation_en": "My friend still can't drive very well, so he always takes the MRT to work.",
      "translation_ko": "제 친구는 아직 운전을 잘 못해서 항상 지하철을 타고 출근해요."
    },
    {
      "text": "我已經學中文半年了，可是還不太會聽懂。",
      "pinyin": "Wǒ yǐjīng xué Zhōngwén bàn nián le, kěshì hái bù tài huì tīng dǒng.",
      "pinyin_numeric": "wo3 yi3jing1 xue2 Zhong1wen2 ban4 nian2 le0, ke3shi4 hai2 bu4 tai4 hui4 ting1 dong3.",
      "translation_en": "I have been studying Chinese for half a year, but I still can't understand it very well.",
      "translation_ko": "저는 중국어를 반 년 동안 배웠지만, 아직 잘 알아듣지 못해요."
    },
    {
      "text": "他還會不太會游泳，所以去海邊的時候要小心。",
      "pinyin": "Tā hái bù tài huì yóuyǒng, suǒyǐ qù hǎibiān de shíhou yào xiǎoxīn.",
      "pinyin_numeric": "ta1 hai2 bu4 tai4 hui4 you2yong3, suo3yi3 qu4 hai3bian1 de0 shi2hou yao4 xiao3xin1.",
      "translation_en": "He still can't swim very well, so he needs to be careful when going to the beach.",
      "translation_ko": "그는 아직 수영을 잘 못해서 해변에 갈 때 조심해야 해요."
    },
    {
      "text": "我哥哥還不太會說英文，可是他每天都努力練習。",
      "pinyin": "Wǒ gēge hái bù tài huì shuō Yīngwén, kěshì tā měitiān dōu nǔlì liànxí.",
      "pinyin_numeric": "wo3 ge1ge hai2 bu4 tai4 hui4 shuo1 Ying1wen2, ke3shi4 ta1 mei3tian1 dou1 nu3li4 lian4xi2.",
      "translation_en": "My older brother still can't speak English very well, but he practices hard every day.",
      "translation_ko": "제 오빠는 아직 영어를 잘 못하지만, 매일 열심히 연습해요."
    },
    {
      "text": "你還會不太會用悠遊卡嗎？我可以幫你。",
      "pinyin": "Nǐ hái bù tài huì yòng Yōuyóukǎ ma? Wǒ kěyǐ bāng nǐ.",
      "pinyin_numeric": "ni3 hai2 bu4 tai4 hui4 yong4 You1you2ka3 ma0? wo3 ke3yi3 bang1 ni3.",
      "translation_en": "Do you still not know how to use the EasyCard very well? I can help you.",
      "translation_ko": "아직 유유카드를 잘 사용하지 못하세요? 제가 도와드릴 수 있어요."
    },
    {
      "text": "她還不太會跳舞，可是她覺得很有意思，所以繼續學。",
      "pinyin": "Tā hái bù tài huì tiàowǔ, kěshì tā juéde hěn yǒu yìsi, suǒyǐ jìxù xué.",
      "pinyin_numeric": "ta1 hai2 bu4 tai4 hui4 tiao4wu3, ke3shi4 ta1 jue2de hen3 you3 yi4si, suo3yi3 ji4xu4 xue2.",
      "translation_en": "She still can't dance very well, but she finds it very interesting, so she continues learning.",
      "translation_ko": "그녀는 아직 춤을 잘 추지 못하지만, 아주 재미있다고 생각해서 계속 배워요."
    }
  ]
}
